description:
Remember, while playing with numbers is fun, the real value of your friendships lies within the quality of the friendships you have, and not the number of friends you have. Quality is more important than the quantity in many areas in life, and friendships are no exception to that.  #inanutshell #kurzgesagt #kurzgesagt_inanutshell #learnwithyoutube #science #friendships #friends #mentalhealth #mentalhealthawareness #friendshipparadox #sociology #psychology #socialpsychology #makingfriends #scienceshorts #learnonyoutube
